General.Name: Aml3d Pty Ltd
General.Description: AML3D Limited provides contract manufacturing services to the aerospace, marine, defence, oil and gas, mining, and general manufacturing sectors in Australia, Singapore, and the United States. The company produces metal components and structures through automated wire-fed 3D printing technology. It designs and constructs ARCEMY 3D printing modules, and 3D parts using wire additive manufacturing technology. AML3D Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Edinburgh, Australia.
